    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s a total dream. This car has been pampered since day one\u2014always garage-kept and looking like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s in truly pristine condition, inside and out, and drives like a charm. If you're looking for something that feels brand new and has been loved every mile, this is the one for you. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 44500.0,
