    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine Carbon Black Metallic. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies to deliver 333hp through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. The mechanical integrity is absolute: the VANOS system has been professionally overhauled, rod bearings replaced, and the rear subframe reinforced with Turner Motorsport plates. Handling remains sharp via the factory M-tuned MacPherson/multi-link suspension and a 3.64:1 M Variable Differential Lock. With zero pixel degradation in the instrument cluster and an impeccable interior, this is a turn-key specimen for the serious collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
