    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a true automotive time capsule. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, retaining its original showroom luster. The exterior paint is flawless, protected by a multi-stage ceramic coating that highlights the deep, mirror-like finish\u2014completely free of stone chips, swirls, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition; the premium leather upholstery is supple and without a single crease, still carrying that distinct new-car scent. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced climate control, functions exactly as it did the day it was delivered. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive, documented service history with all maintenance performed exclusively at certified dealerships. The engine bay is clean enough to eat off of, and the undercarriage shows no signs of road wear or corrosion. With a ride quality that is exceptionally smooth and responsive, this is a collector-grade example for the discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
