    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented in impeccable showroom condition, this vehicle represents the zenith of its model year. Meticulously preserved and maintained to the highest standards, it features a flawless exterior finish complemented by an interior that retains its original luster. This is an investment-grade opportunity for the discerning driver who accepts no compromises in quality or performance. Every mechanical and aesthetic detail has been scrutinized to ensure it meets our most rigorous criteria for excellence.",
      "price": 46500.0,
