    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, this car is in incredible shape\u2014it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, keeping it spotless and strictly following every service milestone. If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 43500.0,
